# Educational Website Rules for AI Code Builders

## ⚠️ MANDATORY PRE-IMPLEMENTATION CHECKLIST ⚠️

1. 📚 EDUCATIONAL REQUIREMENTS VALIDATION
   - [ ] Define course structure
   - [ ] Plan learning paths
   - [ ] Identify user roles
   - [ ] List assessment types
   - [ ] Document learning outcomes

2. 📱 RESPONSIVE DESIGN REQUIREMENTS
   - [ ] Desktop (1920px, 1440px, 1280px)
   - [ ] Tablet (1024px, 768px)
   - [ ] Mobile (428px, 375px, 320px)
   - [ ] Interactive content support

3. 🎯 CORE FEATURES CHECKLIST
   - [ ] Course catalog
   - [ ] Learning management
   - [ ] Progress tracking
   - [ ] Assessment system
   - [ ] Discussion forums
   - [ ] Resource library
   - [ ] Certificate generation
   - [ ] Student dashboard

## 🏗️ Architecture Guidelines

### Component Structure
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── layout/
│   │   ├── Header.tsx
│   │   ├── Footer.tsx
│   │   └── Navigation.tsx
│   ├── courses/
│   │   ├── CourseCard.tsx
│   │   ├── CourseDetail.tsx
│   │   ├── LessonPlayer.tsx
│   │   └── Progress.tsx
│   ├── learning/
│   │   ├── VideoPlayer.tsx
│   │   ├── Quiz.tsx
│   │   ├── Assignment.tsx
│   │   └── Resources.tsx
│   ├── student/
│   │   ├── Dashboard.tsx
│   │   ├── Progress.tsx
│   │   └── Certificates.tsx
│   ├── instructor/
│   │   ├── CourseBuilder.tsx
│   │   ├── Analytics.tsx
│   │   └── Gradebook.tsx
│   └── common/
│       ├── SearchBar.tsx
│       ├── Discussion.tsx
│       └── Notifications.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── courses/
│   ├── learn/
│   ├── dashboard/
│   └── resources/
└── styles/
    └── theme/
```

### Learning Structure
1. **Course Format**
   - Course overview
   - Learning objectives
   - Module structure
   - Assessment criteria
   - Resources

2. **Content Types**
   - Video lectures
   - Interactive lessons
   - Quizzes/Tests
   - Assignments
   - Discussion topics

3. **Progress Tracking**
   - Course completion
   - Assessment scores
   - Learning path progress
   - Certification status

## 📊 Performance Requirements

1. **Content Delivery**
   - Video streaming
   - Resource downloads
   - Interactive content
   - Offline access

2. **Assessment System**
   - Real-time grading
   - Progress tracking
   - Performance analytics
   - Feedback system

3. **Learning Analytics**
   - Student progress
   - Engagement metrics
   - Course analytics
   - Learning outcomes

## 🎓 Learning Experience

1. **Interactive Features**
   - In-video quizzes
   - Practice exercises
   - Discussion forums
   - Live sessions

2. **Progress Visualization**
   - Learning path maps
   - Progress indicators
   - Achievement badges
   - Performance graphs

## 👨‍🏫 Instructor Tools

